Class FeatureExtractor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.wso2.carbon.la.anomalydetection.Operations.FeatureExtractor

  • public class FeatureExtractor
extends Object
    This class splits record beans, splits them according to time windows, and create feature vector of dimension 7.
